item.title: How Coconut Oil Is Sabotaging Your Weight Loss Goals

item.title: John Legend Launches Campaign To End Mass Incarceration
item.description: The ever-philanthropic John Legend is putting his celebrity to good use yet again. The Grammy and Oscar award-winning singer has launched a campaign to end mass incarceration. Dubbed FREE AMERICA, the multi-year initiative will find  Legend performing at a correctional facility in Texas and participating in a press conference with state legislators this week (Apr. 16). “We have a serious problem with incarceration in this country,” Legend told the Huffington Post. “It’s destroying families, it’s destroying communities and we’re the most incarcerated country in the world, and when you look deeper and look at the reasons we got to this place, we as a society made some choices politically and legislatively, culturally to deal with poverty, deal with mental illness in a certain way and that way usually involves using incarceration.

With that in mind, it makes a certain amount of sense that just like Gibson, there have been three different women that Costner was linked to and he has children with all of them.

item.title: Ann Druyan Biography, Age, Family, Education, Carl Sagan, Quotes, Books And Net Worth
item.description: Ann Druyan Biography Ann Druyan is a American writer and producer specializing in the communication of science. She became fame after she co-wrote the 1980 PBS documentary series Cosmos, hosted by Carl Sagan, whom she married in 1981. Ann is the creator, producer, and writer of the 2014 sequel, Cosmos: A Spacetime Odyssey. Ann was the Creative Director of NASA’s Voyager Interstellar Message Project, the golden discs affixed to both the Voyager 1 and Voyager 2 spacecraft.

item.title: Britney Spears Reportedly Wants Another Baby Amid Divorce After Her Sons Move Away
item.description: Highlights Britney Spears is allegedly eager to expand her family by having another baby via a sperm donor, according to reports. She is concerned about financial exploitation from potential partners and is reportedly still dating a former employee. Britney's management team disapproves of her relationship due to the criminal history of her rumored boyfriend, Paul Richard Soliz. Britney Spears is continuing to navigate her divorce from Sam Asghari as well as her complicated relationship with her sons, who moved out-of-state with their dad Kevin Federline to Hawaii without a challenge from their famous mom.

item.title: Did Jordin Sparks Almost Divorce Her Husband Dana Isaiah?
item.description: Life can get messy sometimes, and not even the rich and famous are exempt. Unfortunately for celebrities, their ups and downs, highs and lows are out in the public for strangers to feast on. One such celeb is Jordin Sparks, and the singer is no stranger to negative press. From her breakup with Jason Derulo years ago to her whirlwind relationship with husband Dana Isaiah, people want to know what's happening in Sparks' love life.

item.title: Dog the Bounty Hunter: I Just 'Discovered' I Have a Son Named Jon
item.description: Duane “Dog the Bounty Hunter” Chapman recently learned he fathered a son whose birthday lands on a significant day to the reality star. “For the last four years, this day was a terrible reminder of one of the greatest losses of my life,” Dog, 70, wrote via Instagram on Monday, June 26, which is the fourth anniversary of the death of late wife Beth Chapman. “But God redeemed this day when I discovered my son Jon, who I just met recently, was born on this day.

item.title: Fab Morvan Net Worth How Much is Fab Morvan Worth?
item.description: Fab Morvan, the French singer-songwriter, dancer, and model, has gained significant recognition in the music industry throughout his career. As a member of the pop duo Milli Vanilli, he achieved great success, only to face a major scandal that impacted his reputation. Despite the setback, Fab Morvan continued to pursue his passion for music, carving out a solo career that has endeared him to fans around the world. But just how much is Fab Morvan worth?

item.title: Fans Think This Was Monicas Worst Moment On Friends
item.description: Few shows in TV history were are big as Friends was during its peak years on the small screen. Things weren't always smooth behind the scenes, and some guests were tough to deal with, but each week, the show listened to its audience, and it was able to keep its place at the top for years on end. The show had amazing characters, and they all made great contributions to the show's legacy.

item.title: These Celebrities Want To Be Bradley Cooper's Next Girlfriend
item.description: There's an endless thirst for Bradley Cooper. Of course, fans think the Hangover and A Star Is Born actor is just about the hottest star in Hollywood. But so do several celebrities. Bradley has certainly dated his fair share of famous women, namely his baby-mama model Irina Shayk who he's currently co-parenting his daughter with. But Bradley's relationship history also includes actor Jennifer Esposito, model Suki Waterhouse, Star Trek star Zoe Saldana, Renee Zellwegger, and he's even had a brief fling with Cameron Diaz.

item.title: Actress Jessica Biel Confesses Her Biggest Regret From Her 20's
item.description: Actress Jessica Biel has recently opened up about what particular regret she has from her slightly younger days. We learned from InStyle that Mrs. Justin Timberlake spoke out about one hiccup in her relatively squeaky clean past that haunts her to this day - her sultry photoshoots and style of dressing. "What sultry Jessica Biel photoshoots?" is what you may be asking yourself right now and you wouldn't be alone. In today's world of half-naked former Disney stars and more nip slips and other wardrobe malfunctions from prominent actresses than we know what to do with, it's not hard to see why risqué behavior from Jessica Biel, never one to make many waves in the media, could have easily slipped under the radar.

item.title: Cher at 63: It's "Rough" Appearing On-Screen With Young Burlesque Co-Stars
item.description: At 63 years old, Cher admits it's not always pretty filming Burlesque with the much younger Christina Aguilera and Kristen Bell. "It's a hard job. You get up at 5 a.m. and you try to look good," she tells Entertainment Tonight. "All these girls are, like, a third my age. That is rough." Forget their age! These stars are still hot in a bikini Cher is impressed with her less experienced co-stars though.

item.title: Gossip Girl News - Us Weekly
item.description: Network:The CW Based on the book series of the same name by Cecily von Ziegesar, Gossip Girl revolves around the lives of upper-class teens living in New York City. The series is narrated by an anonymous blogger (voiced by Kristen Bell) who receives tips about characters’ personal lives and spills their secrets online. The show starts with Serena van der Woodsen (Blake Lively) returning to Manhattan after a mysterious absence.
